Can you shut up?

614
00:26:32,320 --> 00:26:33,280
Ma Yiming,

615
00:26:33,920 --> 00:26:34,600
you're just

616
00:26:34,640 --> 00:26:35,880
favoring Xu Mengyu,

617
00:26:35,920 --> 00:26:36,600
do you know that?

618
00:26:36,680 --> 00:26:37,360
