653
00:28:10,960 --> 00:28:12,480
King of the beasts.

654
00:28:16,120 --> 00:28:16,960
King of the table.

655
00:28:17,120 --> 00:28:18,080
What do you see here?

656
00:28:18,160 --> 00:28:19,560
C'mon, look!

657
00:28:21,040 --> 00:28:23,040
Why are you ignoring me?

658
00:28:23,640 --> 00:28:24,320
Is it not good enough?

659
00:28:24,400 --> 00:28:24,920
Lan Jinghui.

